- `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces` - Generates DeepCopy implementations
- `+deepequal-gen:private-method` - Generates custom equality checks (ignores LastAppliedConfig annotation)
- `scope="Namespaced"` - Resource is namespace-scoped
- `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` - Separate status subresource
- `+deepequal-gen=false` on TypeMeta/ObjectMeta - Skips generation for metadata fields
- Methods include: `Parse()`, `GetIdentityLabels()`, `RequiresDerivative()`

